            <ul id="ul_nsz_srb_yz">
                <li>Project description, includes elements for describing the overall project.</li>
                <li>Needs analysis, includes elements for describing organizational needs, audience needs, and the environment for delivering the training.</li>
                <li>Gap analysis </li>
                <li>approach and strategies </li>
                <li>Technical requirements</li>
            </ul>
